texts.text: So this is the Aura Gate in question. The fog is very thick here...
I can't see anything in front of me. We need to be careful.
It might be better to rely on our ears more than our eyes in this situation.
Keep your ears open and listen for anything that doesn't sound right.

Weird sounds...?
Hmm...

Hey, over there!
I think I heard... Wah!
That's just a wall. Also, I didn't say anything about keeping your eyes closed!

Ears open...?
Yo, I'm ain't pickin' up anythin'.
Y'all doin' any better?
I can hear just fine.

Great, partner!
Unfortunately, I can't!
But the rest of us are up a creek...
Okay, Vince, you lead and we'll follow.
So now I'm your meat shield? Thanks a lot.
Just think of it as having your rear covered extremely well.
Fine, whatever. Let's go.
Hold up, everyone...

Yo, what's up?
You hear somethin'?

Yeah, over there.
Sounds like a battle...
A big one too. Like a bunch of people are fighting each other.
Can you hear it...?
Not at all...
Meat Balloon, take us towards the source of that noise.
Copy that. Everyone, try to deaden your footsteps as much as possible.
>As Gakuto leads, the sounds of a battle starts becoming more audible.
Here we are... Whoa!
>You see countless demons clashing in a massive battle.
Die!
Guh...!

*Roar*
How dare you!
*Groan*
W-What the hell's going on here...?

This battle...
Are only demons fighting here?
This is something far worse...
Look.
>Gakuto points to two locations with two separate demons stand.
Dammit, what is 5th Company doing! Keep pressing the line!
Ah, the map is finished... We must strike at once!
Those demons look identical...
Not only that, they seem to be commanding all those demons...
Now I get it. This isn't just some skirmish or scuffle.
Their armies are locked in battle. This is a war...

What do we do...?
Should we stop them?
You plan on diving into that mess of demons?
You must have a death wish or something.
Yo, let's just sit back and enjoy the show for now.
In that case, let's move. They'll see us if we stay here.
Humans! I see humans!

Crap!
Already?!

Damn, sorry!
We got too close!
Should we report this?!
No, they might be hostile! Kill them!
So that's how it's gonna be! Devil Download!
>The Liberators make quick work of the demons. However...

We need backup!
Call for reinforcements!
They are stronger than they look! Attack all at once and not individually!

*Wince*
They're working together...?!
Don't look now but there's more coming!

Yo, this is bad...
Ain't there a way outta here?
Out of this fog? Fat chance. We'll get split apart in seconds!
We just gotta keep fighting and hope that their reinforcements don't come.

There they are!
Is this there the humans are?!

Dammit, they're here...!
Yo, how long is this gonna last...!
Stand down, humans.
Huh?!
*Roar*
>A demon suddenly appears before the Liberators,
>and unleashes a furious attack that sweeps away all of the demons.
W-What just happened...?
It killed all those demons with just one attack!
Wait, we just saw this demon...!
You were using demons just now, were you not...?

Who are you?
What are you doing here?
Yo, we're the Liberators.
And we're investigatin' what's goin' on with this Aura Gate.
Investigating? I see.
To think that such pathetic humans would willingly dabble in the affairs of demons...
Sorry that we're so pathetic, your highness!
My apologies. You fought valiantly against those demons just now.
But why are such peaceful humans engaging in such a battle...?
Huh? Hey, you talking to us or yourself?
Liberators...
What do you plan on doing now that you know what is happening within this Aura Gate?
Yo, we ain't exactly 100% sure about what's really goin' on here...
But we know that this place is havin' a bad effect on our world.

I see...
Yes, I understand.
In that case, Liberators, protectors of humanity, you must listen carefully.
I am Chi You, the god of war.
If you wish to stop whatever it is that is happening to your world,
I shall aid thee.
